{"tid":897564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地邊防部隊涉佔用香港土地 沙頭角建橋擅自過境","createTime":"2018-11-11T04:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T08:58:47.000Z","uid":69930,"like":90,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"3c38e7a564b4b5852f781cdcb5c0a4bccd0ba4d0","tid":897564,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cFKw4xm7NMQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcFKw4xm7NMQ&d=fWDTv%2FdfIQUuWDzsGBvUNTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=354fc883\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cFKw4xm7NMQ</a><br />\n<br />\n內地邊防人員涉嫌越境佔用香港土地。香港沙頭角邊境禁區內一幅面積約兩萬呎土地，被廣東邊防部隊佔用最少6年，並<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>圍封開墾作農田，香港業主並不知情</strong></span>。內地人員更自行建橋過沙頭角河，未經出入境程序進出香港範圍。FactWire傳真社調查期間，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目睹部隊人員多次自由進出香港邊境，包括越境倒垃圾</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/single-post/2018/11/11/內地邊防部隊涉佔用香港土地-沙頭角建橋擅自過境\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fsingle-post%2F2018%2F11%2F11%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%82%8A%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E6%B6%89%E4%BD%94%E7%94%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0-%E6%B2%99%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92%E5%BB%BA%E6%A9%8B%E6%93%85%E8%87%AA%E9%81%8E%E5%A2%83&d=fWDTv%2FdfIQUuWDzsGBvUNTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=96e8ad72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/single-post/2018/11/11/內地邊防部隊涉佔用香港土地-沙頭角建橋擅自過境</a>"},{"pid":"19696852657ceae596969932d9ad7e7a8dd7c89c","tid":897564,"uid":69930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"好想知政府點處理"},{"pid":"f34136f6341c6cf025ca0822689ede651af16fd4","tid":897564,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce123c60047cb59225f8e87484ce75f77d5c3b2d","tid":897564,"uid":125026,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"19696852657ceae596969932d9ad7e7a8dd7c89c","tid":897564,"uid":69930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"