過邊文章<br />\n話中港分界係以深圳河嘅中間作為界限<br />\n咁初時冇乜嘢，但係深圳政府同香港渠務署開始係咁修葺河道<br />\n而每次修葺都係攞香港嗰邊嘅土地嚟掘河<br />\n換言之即係香港嘅土地係咁俾大陸<br />\n到後來深圳政府整咗個深圳河整治（支那字）委員會<br />\n深圳政府嘅干預程度就少啲<br />\n之後就係咁攞係咁囉<br />\n香港政府就係咁送係咁送"},{"pid":"92230e39d59b749d8e3f30a8a96092852c8e764e","tid":897564,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"後海灣<br />\n深圳灣口岸都係香港出錢大陸用，近期就高鐵站每人每日一舊水飯錢"},{"pid":"dfb0add3521df52eb96437ab17d2c189570cfdec","tid":897564,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"中國人民無權知道中國版圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca84df1b3948787e2b7846d2375cd6a010398dd0","tid":897564,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭老公係北京<br />\n<br />\n比人摙住個春袋你覺得佢會出聲？"},{"pid":"985dedc3b1772a877f477e1a4e817356fd567b36","tid":897564,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母自出自入仲要倒埋垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係私人土地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcccb9f161a38d29c80ee08c065fd83b654ae55a","tid":897564,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"明恰到香港人上心口"},{"pid":"4d7d316ea2114c99260c5b90193744d2da22b2e0","tid":897564,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:57:44.000Z","msg":"就算老解黎屠城，呢個廢政府都唔敢吠架啦"},{"pid":"ab6f07f56cfcf533459ce66b7da89d999281f4db","tid":897564,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}